OL,3,CReform councillor faces court after
OL,4,Calleged assault at Pride event
OL,6,FA Reform councillor due to appear in
OL,7,Fcourt after being arrested for assault
OL,8,Fand criminal damage at a Pride event
OL,9,Fin Cheshire.
OL,11,FMandy Clare, who represents Winsford
OL,12,FDene for Reform UK on Cheshire West
OL,13,Fand Chester Council, was arrested at
OL,14,Fthe Winsford Pride event on 28 June.
OL,16,FClare, of Malpas, was bailed and is
OL,17,Fdue to appear at Crewe Magistrates'
OL,18,FCourt on Friday, 8 August.
