OL,6,FThe 54-year-old is currently employed
OL,7,Fin the office of Sarah Pochin, the
OL,8,FReform MP for Runcorn and Helsby, but
OL,9,Fa spokesman for Mrs Pochin said Clare
OL,10,Fhad been suspended pending the outcome
OL,11,Fof criminal proceedings.
OL,13,FThe spokesman said: "On June 29 we
OL,14,Fwere made aware of serious allegations
OL,15,Finvolving a member of staff. She was
OL,16,Fimmediately suspended from her
OL,17,Fposition pending the outcome of the
OL,18,Finvestigation."
